****** CLASS 3 ******

1] What are Variables?
       Variables are containers or boxes in the memory that can hold/ store the data.

2] Why we Need Variables?
       To access the data ie store into the variable later.

3] How to create the Variables (syntax)?
       First- declare the correct Data type for the variable (eg: for whole number- byte/short/int/long)
       second- Name the variable